 Following the SOPA address, the Gauteng Provincial Budget will be announced next week. Gauteng MEC for Finance, Barbara Creecy tells CNBC Africa’s Karabo Lethlathla about some of the key priority areas in the budget – and finally, ANC Provincial secretary Hope Papo shares his thoughts on the criminal justice system, education, economic growth, job creation and skills development and against the backdrop of the SOPA. 